{"tid":335582,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"ＨＫＢＮ　１１月完","createTime":"2017-07-25T16:21:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-26T07:49:38.000Z","uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"59e154d549cbbdbfd33de5d2501c8dc11abf7e24","tid":335582,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T16:21:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請問呢家和記得唔得</span></span><br />\n住既地頭因為好濕<br />\n入得ＨＫＢＮ同３兩間<br />\n仲要係兩間都得１００ＭＢ<br />\n想轉ＮＥＶＥＲ基他或ＰＣＣＷ都無得間<br />\n<br />\n我諗因為咁<br />\nＨＫＢＮ都幾肯定覺得我會頂唔順３唔會轉咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呻多下<br />\n年頭記起兩年約<br />\n上網諗住續<br />\n１８Ｘ<br />\n屌你老母乜尻ＭＹＴＶＳＵＰＥＲ<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n年中問啦<br />\n係都要１６Ｘ＋ＭＹＴＶＳＵＰＥＲ<br />\n屌住問可唔可以唔要三色台垃圾平少少服務下舊客<br />\nＳＯＲＲＹ，公司規定，屌<br />\n<br />\n呢家續都係１５Ｘ<br />\n求個心安，想轉和記１００<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d7267436707dbad46160999b6115bf43ffda7a4","tid":335582,"uid":7452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T16:26:32.000Z","msg":"屌晒你地全部人"},{"pid":"5d021b520b0c482f9ddc08d6d7bc67dcd937d439","tid":335582,"uid":129680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T16:36:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"445b33815863c0f8503413541761f6ad35fa0b20","tid":335582,"uid":124853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T16:44:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"66e1a5b4c62f8ced45ac1a8425c1fe74061c0880","tid":335582,"uid":129678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T16:48:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c63dae410f5903a25723963540a32e29f00ed797","tid":335582,"uid":115853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T16:53:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe58461dbc3f3139b057e8f101c419c54b701f9e","tid":335582,"uid":1